translate french dana3_96b67724:

    # "I shut the door immediately and step back, closing my eyes, trying to push what I saw out of my mind."
    "Je ferme la porte immédiatement et recule, fermant les yeux, essayant de chasser de mon esprit ce que j’ai vu."

